Yes, I did think the trailer for The Basement was better than the actual show!  For those who haven't seen it, here is the script as far as I recall:

"I've got thirty seconds to tell you about my new show.  We film it down 'ere - C'mon!" [The Basement]
"Which is also a working boozer.  We've got balls - footballs, guests and... Cow Pat Bingo!  Match your dumpling to a cow pat on a grid"
(Then some woman says something which I can't actually remember)
"The Basement, 'cos it's the basement.  Be there, weeknights 10.30 on Bravo."
@endnode

